(2. THE PRIME DIRECTIVE) show newline
(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(    "If it's in the TCB, it's in OCaml. Otherwise it's in Chicken Scheme.") show newline
() show newline
() show newline
